### =============================================
### AUTH TESTS
### =============================================

### =============================================
### VARIABLES
### =============================================

@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@userPassword = TestUser123!
@adminPassword = AdminUser123!

@userToken = PASTE_USER_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

@taskId = 1
@userId = 2


### =============================================
### STEP 1 — Run these first every time
### =============================================

### Get USER token — copy response token to {{userToken}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password":"{{userPassword}}"
}

###

### Get ADMIN token — copy response token to {{adminToken}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}


### 1. Register a new user (should work — 201)
