### =============================================
### TASK TESTS — replace {{userToken}} below
### =============================================

### 9. Create a task successfully (should get 200 with task JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "Build the login page",
  "description": "Create a responsive login form with validation",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "deadline": "2030-06-30"
}

###

### 10. Create another task to have data for later tests
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "Write unit tests",
  "description": "Cover all service layer methods",
  "priority": "MEDIUM",
  "deadline": "2030-12-31"
}

###

### 11. Create task with no title (should get 400 with field error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "This should fail",
  "priority": "LOW"
}

###

### 12. Get my tasks (should return tasks you just created)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/my
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 13. Update task status to IN_PROGRESS (use id 1 — change if different)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/status?status=IN_PROGRESS
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 14. Update task status to COMPLETED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/status?status=COMPLETED
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 15. Try invalid status value (should get 400 with clear message)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/status?status=DONE
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 16. Try to get a task that does not exist (should get 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 17. Update full task details (use id 2)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "Write unit tests — updated",
  "description": "Cover service and controller layers",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "deadline": "2030-07-20"
}

###

### 18. Try accessing tasks without token (should get 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/my

