### =============================================
### WEEK 7 — REFRESH TOKEN TESTS
### =============================================

### Login — response now has accessToken AND refreshToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password":"{{userPassword}}"
}

###

### Use refresh token to get new access token
### Paste the refreshToken value from login response below
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Use the same refresh token again — should get 400
### Because token rotation invalidated it
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout — invalidates the refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Try to refresh after logout — should get 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Try refresh with a fake token — should get 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "this-is-not-a-real-token"
}
